Package org.eclipse.jetty.client

Class ProxyConfiguration

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.jetty.client.ProxyConfiguration
public class ProxyConfiguration extends Object

The configuration of the forward proxies to use with HttpClient.

Applications add subclasses of ProxyConfiguration.Proxy to this configuration via, for example:


 ProxyConfiguration proxyConfig = httpClient.getProxyConfiguration();
 proxyConfig.addProxy(new HttpProxy(proxyHost, 8080));
